de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.sensorwrapper

Interface SensorWrapper<T extends de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.sensor.Sensor<?>>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSensorWrapper, CC2650Wrapper, HeartRateSensorWrapper, PulseOximeterSensorWrapper

    public interface SensorWrapper<T extends de.fhg.fit.biomos.sensorplatform.sensor.Sensor<?>>
    Defines an Interface for interacting with the Sensorplatform. This API may be expanded, for example: Add reading of battery status, get intended position of the sensor on the human body, ... The Sensorplatform in its current state utilises only a small subset of what it is possible or supported by the Bluetooth specification.
    Author:
    Daniel Pyka
